05": ["paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "frontend-2", "checkoutservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-19T18:10:03Z to 2025-06-19T18:34:03Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-19 18:10:03+00:00 to 2025-06-19 18:34:03+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["emailservice-1", "frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "frontend-0", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "frontend-2", "checkoutservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "io_util", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的日志数据，我现在进行初始扫描分析。从日志中可以看到，所有错误都来自frontend服务，主要涉及两种类型的错误模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"context canceled\", \"failed to get product\", \"rpc error\", \"Canceled\", \"Internal\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"产品目录服务无法响应产品信息查询，导致frontend服务在结账时无法获取产品信息，出现failed to get product错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\\\"0PUK6V6EV0\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"结账服务处理超时或上下文取消，导致订单处理失败，出现context canceled错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析发现**：\n\n1. **主要错误模式**：\n   - **产品信息获取失败**：frontend服务无法从产品目录服务获取产品信息（出现29+26+2+2+13+1=73次）\n   - **上下文取消错误**：订单处理过程中上下文被取消（出现7+5+5+3=20次）\n\n2. **关键观察**：\n   - 所有错误都来自frontend服务，但问题根源可能在下游服务\n   - 错误集中在结账流程（/cart/checkout路径）\n   - 涉及多个frontend实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）和节点\n\n3. **初步假设**：\n   - productcatalogservice可能是根因，因为大量错误涉及产品信息获取失败\n   - checkoutservice可能存在处理延迟问题，导致上下文超时取消\n\n需要进一步分析Trace数据来验证这些假设，特别是查看frontend到下游服务的调用链路状态。", "trace_analysis_findings": "Based on the trace data analysis for the system fault during 2025-06-19T18:10:03Z to 2025-06-19T18:34:03Z, I've identified significant anomalies in the call chain. Here's my analysis:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->emailservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService调用ProductCatalogService/GetProduct的延迟从正常14.9ms激增至27.7秒，延迟倍数达1855倍，出现43次异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend调用CheckoutService/PlaceOrder的延迟从正常155ms激增至27.5秒，延迟倍数达176倍，出现31次异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"状态码显示大量连接超时错误：'timed out waiting for server handshake' (40次)和'connection error: i/o timeout' (34次)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService调用PaymentService/Charge的延迟从正常13.9ms增至69.1ms，延迟倍数约5倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService调用EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation的延迟从正常24.5ms增至71.6ms，延迟倍数约3倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **根因定位**: ProductCatalogService是系统故障的主要根源，表现为严重的连接超时和极高的延迟增长。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**: \n   - ProductCatalogService故障 → CheckoutService无法获取商品信息 → PlaceOrder失败 → Frontend返回500错误\n\n3. **影响范围**: 故障影响了整个订单流程，导致大量订单失败（HTTP 500错误）。\n\n4. **次要影响**: PaymentService和EmailService也出现延迟增长，但幅度相对较小，可能是由于系统整体负载增加导致的连锁反应。\n\n建议优先检查ProductCatalogService的健康状态、网络连接和资源利用率。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对故障期间指标数据的全面分析，我发现了多个显著的异常模式。以下是初始扫描阶段的发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"io_util\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio和client_error_ratio指标出现严重异常，错误率从0%飙升到50-60%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0的error_ratio从正常中位数0.0上升到故障中位数50.0，p99从0.0上升到60.0，变化率均为2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio和client_error_ratio指标异常，错误率显著上升\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-0的error_ratio p99从0.0上升到47.57，变化率为2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt和rrt_max指标严重恶化，响应时间大幅增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0的rrt从正常中位数11526.1上升到故障中位数108091.39，rrt_max从228009.0飙升到20014272.5，变化率分别达到1.6146和1.9549\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt和rrt_max指标异常，响应时间显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice-1的rrt从正常中位数7087.3上升到故障中位数1969946.54，rrt_max从206433.0上升到20011731.0，变化率分别为1.9857和1.9592\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend集群\",\n      \"reason\": \"所有frontend实例的rrt_max指标均出现严重恶化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0/1/2的rrt_max分别从228009/235878/254944上升到20014272/20014853/20013127，变化率均超过1.94\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"io_util指标出现异常波动，可能影响数据库性能\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-tikv的io_util p99从正常0.12上升到故障0.27，变化率0.7661\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n\n1. **服务错误率激增**：shippingservice-0和cartservice-0出现严重的错误率异常\n2. **响应时间严重恶化**：frontend和checkoutservice的响应时间指标出现数量级增长\n3. **数据库IO异常**：tidb-tikv的IO利用率出现波动\n4. **前端服务普遍受影响**：所有frontend实例都出现响应时间问题，表明问题可能具有系统性\n\n这些异常模式表明系统在故障期间经历了严重的性能降级和错误率上升，需要进一步分析以确定根本原因。"}
