ppingservice` 和 `cartservice`）可能是由于 `productcatalogservice` 的故障引起的依赖问题。\n\n### 结论\n基于以上分析，`productcatalogservice` 的严重连接超时和延迟峰值是系统故障的根因。因此，我支持该假设。\n\n### 输出结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段平均延迟从14.9ms增加到27.7s，延迟倍数1855倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"频繁出现超时错误（74次）和连接错误\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "9d5029d9-385", "component": "productcatalogservice", "reason": "rrt_max spike from 14.9ms to 27.7s (1855x) and connection timeout errors causing frontend failures", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(productcatalogservice)", "observation": "rrt_max increased from 14.9ms to 27.7s, 1855x latency spike during fault window"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LogSearch(frontend)", "observation": "Found 75 failed to get product errors and context canceled logs indicating productcatalogservice timeout"}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(9d5029d9-385)", "observation": "checkoutservice->productcatalogservice and frontend->productcatalogservice calls timing out with rrt_max anomalies"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
